<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Check-out Reminder - PropSisters</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd7e14 0%, #dc3545 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .reminder-details {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #fd7e14;
        }
        .checkout-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .checklist {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #fd7e14;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üè† Check-out Reminder</h1>
        <p>Your stay is ending soon</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= user.name || user.email %>!</h2>
        <p>We hope you've enjoyed your stay at <strong><%= property.title %></strong>! Your check-out is approaching.</p>
        
        <div class="checkout-info">
            <h3>üìÖ Check-out Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Check-out Date:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= checkOutDate %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Property:</strong> <%= property.title %></p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= property.location %></p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> <%= propertyAddress %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist">
            <h3>‚úÖ Check-out Checklist</h3>
            <p>Please ensure you have completed the following before leaving:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Remove all personal belongings</li>
                <li>Clean up any mess or trash</li>
                <li>Turn off all lights and electronics</li>
                <li>Lock all doors and windows</li>
                <li>Return any keys or access cards</li>
                <li>Check all rooms and closets</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reminder-details">
            <h3>üîë Check-out Instructions</h3>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Please vacate the property by the scheduled check-out time</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Contact the property owner if you need to arrange a different time</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Leave the property in the same condition you found it</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Follow any specific check-out procedures provided by the owner</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reminder-details">
            <h3>üìû Contact Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Property Owner:</strong> <%= property.ownerName %></p>
            <p><strong>Owner Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:<%= property.ownerPhone %>"><%= property.ownerPhone %></a></p>
            <p><strong>Owner Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:<%= property.ownerEmail %>"><%= property.ownerEmail %></a></p>
            <p><strong>PropSisters Support:</strong> <%= process.env.ADMIN_EMAIL || 'admin@propsisters.com' %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reminder-details">
            <h3>‚≠ê Feedback Request</h3>
            <p>We would love to hear about your experience! Please consider:</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Leaving a review for the property</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Rating your overall experience</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Sharing any feedback or suggestions</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Recommending us to friends and family</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reminder-details">
            <h3>üîÑ Future Bookings</h3>
            <p>Thank you for choosing PropSisters! We hope to welcome you back soon.</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Browse our other amazing properties</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Book your next getaway</p>
            <p>‚Ä¢ Follow us for special offers</p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
            <strong>Thank you for being a valued PropSisters guest!</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2024 PropSisters. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
